<item>
            <title>[SPR-7879] Better abstraction for transactional configuration in DMLC</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-7879</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We experienced a threads leak using Spring&apos;s DMLC on JBoss 4.2.3. We configured our DMLC as follows:&lt;/p&gt;

